00:05:41.742 --> 00:05:43.700
So when you're ready,
just head up to the board

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:45.218
and place your dots on the line.

00:05:45.218 --> 00:05:47.510
And, yes, you do have to vote
for three separate items.

00:05:47.510 --> 00:05:52.128
You can't put all your three
dots on one particular row.

00:05:52.128 --> 00:05:53.920
So go ahead when you're
ready just come up.

