00:06:38.210 --> 00:06:41.240
Excellent, so I think it's
making a difference by quite

00:06:41.240 --> 00:06:47.570
a few lengths there, work
family balance, and then salary.

00:06:47.570 --> 00:06:50.750
So let's see how some of
your answers as a class

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:53.660
compared to some studies
that have been done.

00:06:53.660 --> 00:06:56.150
And this is just
one sample that's

00:06:56.150 --> 00:06:58.060
actually been done by Boeing.

00:06:58.060 --> 00:07:01.010
It's some of their employee
satisfaction surveys.

00:07:01.010 --> 00:07:03.290
And what you see here
on the chart is--

00:07:03.290 --> 00:07:07.010
the x-axis here and the
